snippet.title: The Sims™ 4 Realm of Magic: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a supernatural world and master the art of wizardy in The Sims 4: Realm of Magic!*

Available September 10, 2019 on PC and Mac. Coming to Xbox One and PlayStation 4 on October 15, 2019.

Learn more about this Game Pack: http://x.ea.com/59290.

*REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 GAME (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES TO PLAY. SEE MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THIS PACK.
